<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-9985] Sink connector consuming DLQ topic may exhaust broker</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-9985</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a sink connector is configured with a DLQ and its topic is the same (or matches) as the topic in which the connector reads, the broker and/or connector might be exhausted in case the record send to the topic is invalid.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Based on the broker/connect config, the connector might fail throwing a RecordTooLargeException previous to exhaust the broker/connector.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
